Refrain = \lyricmode {

And He calls, and He calls all the G -- I -- R -- L -- S, \bar "."
And He wants all the B -- O -- Y -- S too, \bar "."
To T -- R -- U -- S -- T in Him, \bar "." % original has melismata here, but why ? for piano ?
